<p>Agar siz hali ro\'yxatdan o\'tmagan bo\'lsangiz va yangiliklar va yangilashlarni olishni istasangiz, <strong>iltimos, <a href="http://pkp.sfu.ca/ojs/register" target="_new">http://pkp.sfu.ca/ojs/register</a>ga ro\'yxatdan o\'ting.</strong> Agar sizning savollaringiz yoki takliflaringiz bolsa, iltimos, <a href="http://forum.pkp.sfu.ca" target="_new">o\'rinbosarlik forumiga</a> tashrif bering.</p>

